- "Dalang pengeboman"?

227
00:18:52,195 --> 00:18:53,571
Berapa lama?

228
00:18:55,198 --> 00:18:57,033
Situasi keamanan Gedung Biru tak stabil.

229
00:18:57,742 --> 00:18:58,826
Jangan buang waktu...

230
00:18:58,910 --> 00:19:00,828
Ini masalah keamanan nasional.

231
00:19:05,875 --> 00:19:08,336
Konspirator pengeboman itu
ada di Gedung Biru.

232
00:19:08,419 --> 00:19:10,004
Itu tidak mungkin.

233
00:19:12,757 --> 00:19:14,467
<i>Kau Menteri Pertahanan Nasional?</i>

234
00:19:14,967 --> 00:19:16,928
<i>Ini Cha Yeong-jin dari Sekretariat.</i>

235
00:19:17,845 --> 00:19:20,431
<i>Tolong cabut izin keamanan
